                            <div>
                                <strong>The author of a message - Playing entity.</strong>
                            </div>
                            <div/>
                            <div>If used in CDA documents or GP Summary (Coded) this is a person however if used in an initial GP Summary (Text-only) this is an organisation. <br/>
                            </div>
