                        <div>
                            <p>
                                <b>The organisation which the author is scoped by.</b>
                            </p>
                            <p>Some messages will only have an associated scoping organisation with no named person as an author player.  <br/>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </text>
                </otherAnnotation>
            </annotations>
            <attribute conformance="R" fixedValue="ORG"
                isMandatory="true" isStructural="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="classCode" sortKey="1">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <p>Indicates this is an organisation.<br/>
                            </p>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="classCode"
                    className="Organization" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
                <type name="CS"/>
                <supplierDomainSpecification codingStrength="CNE" domainName="ORG"/>
            </attribute>
            <attribute conformance="R" fixedValue="INSTANCE"
                isMandatory="true" isStructural="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="determinerCode" sortKey="2">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <p>Indicates this is an instance<br/>
                            </p>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="determinerCode"
                    className="Organization" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
                <type name="CS"/>
                <supplierDomainSpecification codingStrength="CNE" domainName="INSTANCE"/>
            </attribute>
            <attribute conformance="R" isMandatory="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="id" sortKey="3">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <div style="height: 100%; width: 100%">
                                <div>
                                    <div style="height: 100%; width: 100%">
                                    <div>
                                    <p>A valid SDS identifier that uniquely identifies the Organization. The <i>root</i> attribute shall be the OID for the SDS code set  and the <i>extension</i> shall contain the code.<br/>
                                    <br/>For GP Summary an SDS Organization  shall be identified as follows:<br/>
                                    </p>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>The <i>root</i> attribute shall contain an OID with the value  1.2.826.0.1285.0.1.10                           </li>
                                    <li>the <i>extension</i> attribute shall contain the SDS Organisation Id, known in the External Interface Specification as the NACS Organisation Code. </li>
                                    </ul>For CDA documents  an SDS Organization  shall be identified as follows:<br/>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>The <i>root</i> attribute shall contain an OID with the value either 2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.19.2 or 2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.19.1 </li>
                                    <li>the <i>extension</i> attribute shall contain the SDS Organisation Id, known in the External Interface Specification as the NACS Organisation Code. </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="id"
                    className="Organization" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
                <type name="II" typeSpecialisation="II.NPfIT.oid.mandatory"/>
            </attribute>
            <attribute conformance="R" isMandatory="true"
                maximumMultiplicity="1" minimumMultiplicity="1"
                name="name" sortKey="6">
                <annotations>
                    <otherAnnotation type="html">
                        <text>
                            <p>The display name associated with the scoping organisation.<br/>
                            </p>
                        </text>
                    </otherAnnotation>
                </annotations>
                <derivationSupplier attributeName="name"
                    className="Organization" staticModelDerivationId="1"/>
                <type name="ON"/>
            </attribute>
        </class>
    </ownedClass>
