                                <br/> The SDS organisation id attribute can be populated using the following SDS codes:</p> Organisations can be filtered in SDS by using the NACS code for the organisation which is the custodian of the document and the types "nhsOrg" and "nhsGPPractice"<br/>   (Organisations can be either of these)                                      <ul>
